Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到花該是件多高興的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的不是送花的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 誰送花會比較高興？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦 是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉紅害羞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯的那個初夏的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也照舊到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水星大潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去參加鳳尾舟協會的會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚應該就能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天暖洋洋的呢 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是亞利亞公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是本大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在長靴小路等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用超快的速度給我趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用超快的速度哦 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}總覺得有點害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}哎呀 你丈夫送給你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}今天一天都很緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}不知道我能不能收到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:25.28,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 伯克洛節上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸前戴著紅玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子 你太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生 拉頭髮禁止啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不是鬢子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？誰叫你的鬢角這麼多破綻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝了整整一筐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是想啊…送給艾莉西亞小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天是伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 絕佳的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天可是男人給愛慕之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送上一朵玫瑰的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那已經不止一朵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爺對艾莉西亞小姐的崇高的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用一朵花來表達怎麼夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有把全城的玫瑰都買下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能表達我無限的愛意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生一個人拿不了這麼多花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才叫我來幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該覺得光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼小的女孩們也都戴著花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲也收到玫瑰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 是麵包屋的叔叔送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是友情玫瑰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 難道這也是友情玫瑰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你說那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是曉先生要送給艾莉西亞前輩的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為那是燈裏前輩從不同的人那裏收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為雅典娜前輩一大早就收到了一堆玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司的後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 她好像有很多小孩子的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲也送給雅典娜前輩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不送友情玫瑰主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算我送玫瑰給她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只不過是多了一朵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對雅典娜前輩來說 沒有什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得雅典娜前輩會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送給她的話 她會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼涼的石板路好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面上倒映著天空 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晾曬的衣物 建築物的格子窗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還有浮島呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像在鏡子之國裏一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊 讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 哥斯拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准叫我哥斯拉 你這個馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准叫我馬尾男 你這只哥斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥斯拉哥斯拉哥斯拉哥斯拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華也收到玫瑰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是阿魯送的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是阿魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊 是我要送給艾莉西亞前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說馬尾男…那些玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都要送給艾莉西亞前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只有一朵花是無法展現我的心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 燈裏 艾莉西亞前輩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去參加鳳尾舟協會的會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬尾男 我會搶先把花送給艾莉西亞前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 藍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭哥斯拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 本大爺就要用數量壓倒一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿曉～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 燈裏 你好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多玫瑰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這些幾乎都是送給晃前輩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋的晃小姐似乎很受女孩子歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年我都要給她投遞很多玫瑰的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是晃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這是阿曉你托我買的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒給我錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 先欠著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你要拒絕老朋友的請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿曉 你上次借的和上上次借的都還…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候我把脆脆冰中獎的雪糕棒給了你對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別告訴我你不記得這個恩情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…這麼久以前的事情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要中獎的雪糕棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭得滿地打滾的那個是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想我把那件事添油加醋地告訴鬢子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏小姐 我還要幹活 先走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 請加油工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要繼續買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要表達本大爺的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點玫瑰遠遠不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你就不能再便宜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜不了就是便宜不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀你就再便宜一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}我可是全都買光哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯克洛到底是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯克洛是花蕾的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你講講伯克洛節的由來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伯克洛節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男性無論老少都會給愛慕的人送上一朵紅玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個節日的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個傳統的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是數百年前發生在地球上的真實故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一個愛上了高貴姑娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下級貴族青年的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個青年為了向姑娘的父親展示自己的誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就自告奮勇地上了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不幸的青年在戰鬥中受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終體力不支而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他倒下的地方恰好是一片白玫瑰花叢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青年拼盡最後一絲氣力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘下一朵玫瑰交給了戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘收到被青年的鮮血染紅的白玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知了自己的愛人已經戰死的噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是個悲傷的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也很浪漫不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅玫瑰象徵著永恆的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還有這樣一個故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你砍完價了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 本大爺完勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的很不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事的男女主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經在數百年前過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但青年的愛仍舊化作紅色玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直流傳到了今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 鳳尾舟協會的會議剛剛結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢了一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來 在亞利亞公司門前等會比較快吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老家在浮島上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一直在那裏待到昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正準備回地下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水星大潮的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐的公司都放假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是開店歇業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今天還是伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那朵玫瑰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這是我自己買來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想送給艾莉西亞前輩的玫瑰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…我說這是別人送的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯會是什麼樣的表情呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐對寶石有興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寶石？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是怎麼突然想起問這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為「玫瑰之瞳」的寶石原石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地下世界偶爾能挖到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玫瑰之瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過竟然借玫瑰的話題送我寶石原石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…莫非這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 藍華 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊 燈裏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 曉君也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 阿魯 好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 你見到艾莉西亞前輩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這是怎麼回事啊 曉君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多玫瑰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是本大爺為了表達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}比大海還要深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}比浮島還要高遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}對艾莉西亞小姐的愛意才買下的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯送我這塊石頭的含義…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是熱情的氣候調節員 曉君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 晃前輩好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我見到伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他投遞了好多送給晃前輩的玫瑰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…每年都是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐 你發燒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我沒什麼問題啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？剛才？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 還是先幫我找艾莉西亞前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍…藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這樣就做好萬全的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就是送玫瑰的練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子啊 拜託你演一下艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的…心…心…心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習就這麼緊張怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你的表情好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 而且你演的艾莉西亞小姐一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還挺有自信的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看了艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演得不像還這麼緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那見到真人會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會怎麼樣我也無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才拜託你陪我練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們再來一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟協會的會議結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我正準備回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多玫瑰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是工作關繫上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從熟客和聯絡處那裏收到了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這這這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的心…心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 燈裏才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從曉君那裏收到了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打擾你們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…艾 艾莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亞利亞社長！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞小姐！Come back！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Back…back…back…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音 傳不到那邊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是個廢柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋪滿了整個水面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直 延伸到遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像 很久以前那對戀人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映照在人心中蔓延開來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人對另外一個人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那溫柔又略帶哀愁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給每個人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都帶來了和煦的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人不可思議地換上笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色玫瑰的傳說所施下的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐 關於剛才那個玫瑰之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要稍加雕琢就會變得很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的寶石一定很適合藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊也有紅色玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}日語中五花肉與玫瑰有部分發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老頭子的冷笑話 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是地球上流傳已久的文字遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找到艾莉西亞前輩之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要陪著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能傳達給艾莉西亞前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那毫無根據的自信是從哪來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你陪了我一天的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次收到男孩子送的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一朵紅玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說無論是男性還是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到花都會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送上一朵紅玫瑰的伯克洛節
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛開在水星大潮的城市中的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鮮艷的玫瑰紅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯得是那麼的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是個小小的紀念日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐 能度過美好的一天真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色玫瑰的傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是個悲傷的愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有點讓人憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 樸實的星光…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:02:01.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:14.81,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:29.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:42.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:48.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:56.59,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:04.10,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:14.41,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:02:01.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:14.81,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:29.86,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:42.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:48.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:56.59,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艷麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:04.10,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:14.41,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:56.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨が上がる 遠く空眺め 雲の切れ間探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:07.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもよりも 少し遠回り 海へ続く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}切りすぎた前髪 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:20.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そのまま 駆け出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:27.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をかすめていく 風の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.69,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか夏のはじまりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:38.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}大きく手を振って 深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:44.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}この時間を抱きしめていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:49.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}明日もまた会えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:56.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨過天晴 眺望遙遠的天空 探尋雲彩的縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:07.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}繞過早已習慣的歸途 向著通往大海的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}忘掉剪得過短的留海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:20.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}毫無顧忌地大膽前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:27.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}吹拂著面頰的海風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不知何時染上了初夏的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:38.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}用力揮揮手 來個深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:44.54,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}滿心希望永遠擁抱這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:49.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}明天 我們還會再見嗎

